ot auto-repair the ledger; operators or a backlog-repair prompt still need to fix `.ralph/tasks.json`.\n\n```json\n{\n  \"selectedTaskId\": \"T23.2\",\n  \"requestedStatus\": \"done\",\n  \"progressNote\": \"Surfaced task-ledger drift explicitly in preflight summaries, status output, and replenish-backlog prompt selection/strategy so inconsistent ledgers no longer read as clean backlog exhaustion. Added regression coverage for the new wording and prompt decision path.\",\n  \"validationRan\": \"cd ralph-codex-vscode-starter && npm run validate\"\n}\n```\n"}
